
Ctrl + Space :
	    main -> Ctrl + Space -> generate main contustor
	    sysout -> Ctrl + Space -> System.out.println("");
	    syserr -> Ctrl + Space -> System.err.println("");
	    fore -> Ctrl + Space -> generate for each loop code scope
	    Class Name  -> Ctrl + Space -> import class
	    after class name & a space  -> Ctrl + Space -> suggest varial name
	
Ctrl + 1 :   Check error & suggest suggestion
	
Ctrl + Shift + R :  Search file in Resources
	
Ctrl + Shift + T :    Search Type/Class 
	
F3 :    Go to Declearation
	
F4 :    Type Hierarchy
	
Ctrl + Shift + L : List of shortcut

Generating code : Alt + Shift + S

Delete line : Ctrl + D

Duplicate line : Ctrl + Alt + Up

import : Ctrl + Shift + o

Format line : Ctrl + Shift + F

Moving line up : Alt + up arrow

Moving line down : Alt + down arrow



........... eclipse configaration .........................

Save Action:
	window -> perferences ->
		Java -> Editor -> Save Action -> (can set various configaration while save like auto format source code, remove unused variable)

				
Show Different windows:
	window -> show view ->
		to bring different view on screen

window -> perspective ->
		to change differnt view setting

To change fonts :
		window -> perferences ->
			General -> Appearance -> Colors and Fonts
						Basic -> Text Font





